# Copy to .env.local and fill in values. .env.local is gitignored.
#
# On Vercel deployments this is not needed — the AI SDK v6 Gateway uses
# VERCEL_OIDC_TOKEN automatically, which Vercel injects for you. This file
# only matters for local development.
#
# For local dev, create an AI Gateway API key at:
#   https://vercel.com/dashboard/ai-gateway/api-keys
#
# Alternatively, run `vercel env pull .env.local` from this directory to
# fetch a 12-hour OIDC token and any other env vars you've configured in
# the Vercel dashboard.

AI_GATEWAY_API_KEY=
